<p>The Department of Art offers studies in the following areas of emphasis including: Art Education, Art History, Book Arts, Ceramics, Drawing, Graphic Design, Illustration, Painting, Photography, Printmaking and Sculpture. These emphasis areas are designed to provide preparation for a professional career choice as well as personal artistic enjoyment.&nbsp;</p>
<p>This site is designed to provide you with information that will help you to be better informed and complete a program of study more smoothly. Use the navigation menu to the left and quick links below to locate the information that you need.</p>
<p>For additional information on the degrees we offer and our admissions process click on "Degrees" in the column to the left.</p>
<p><strong>If you have any questions you can email us at art_dept@byui.edu&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></p>
